      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Author and edit prompts via UI or CLI\n- Version control with full history\n- Auto-run evals on every change\n- Block deployment if evals fail\n- A/B test prompt variants in prod\n- 1-click rollback to any version",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Author and edit prompts via UI or CLI\n- Version control with full history\n- Auto-run evals on every change\n- Block deployment if evals fail\n- A/B test prompt variants in prod\n- 1-click rollback to any version",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
